# SonarQube Integration

This project has SonarQube integration configured.

## MCP Tools Available

Use these tools via MCP for code quality analysis:

- `sonar_fetch_issues` - Fetch open issues (params: severity, newCode, file)
- `sonar_run_analysis` - Run SonarQube analysis
- `sonar_format_issues` - Format JSON response as table

## When User Asks About Code Quality

1. Use sonar_fetch_issues to get current issues
2. Present in table format: File | Line | Rule | Message | Severity
3. Ask which issues to fix
4. Fix issues one by one, always reading file first
5. Run build after all fixes

## Severity Levels

- BLOCKER: Must fix immediately
- HIGH: Important issues
- MEDIUM: Should fix
- LOW: Nice to fix
- INFO: Informational

## Environment Variables Required

- SONAR_HOST_URL
- SONAR_TOKEN
- SONAR_PROJECT_KEY
